||1
| |[[File:MacArthur_Manila.jpg|75px]]
|| [[道格拉斯·麦克阿瑟|道格拉斯·麦克阿瑟]] 
||1950年6月26日，当时任美国总统的[[杜鲁门|杜鲁门]]下令[[驻日美军|驻日美军]]协助[[大韩民国国军|大韩民国国军]]作战。7月8日，杜鲁门指定麦克阿瑟担任联合国军的指挥官。6天后，李承晚将韓國國軍指挥权交给麦克阿瑟<ref name="Isserman">{{cite book |author=Maurice Isserman |others = 陈昱澍 译 |title= 美国人眼中的朝鲜战争 |location=北京 |publisher=当代中国出版社 |year=2006 |ISBN=7-80170-437-1}}</ref>。9月15日，联合国军在麦克阿瑟的指挥下实行[[仁川登陆|仁川登陆]]。
麦克阿瑟在朝鲜的很多行动都未得到华府的首肯，有些甚至违背华盛顿的决策<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.trumanlibrary.org/trivia/macarth.htm |title=''FAQ: Why did President Truman dismiss General MacArthur?'' |publisher=The Harry S. Truman Library and Museum |accessdate=2017-01-30 |archive-date=2013-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130522095555/http://www.trumanlibrary.org/trivia/macarth.htm |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref>，因而[[杜鲁门总统解职道格拉斯·麦克阿瑟|被免職]]。這項命令是麥克阿瑟在無線電廣播中與全世界民眾一起知悉的。<ref>{{cite book |author=James F Schnabel |date=1972 |title=''Policy and Direction: the First Year. United States Army in the Korean War'' |url=http://www.history.army.mil/books/PD-C-20.HTM |location=Washington, DC |publisher=US Government Printing Office |pages=376–377 |access-date=2017-01-30 |archive-date=2014-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140923045928/http://www.history.army.mil/books/PD-C-20.HTM |dead-url=no }}{{en}}</ref><ref name="James1985">{{cite book|author=Dorris Clayton James|title=''The Years of Macarthur: Triumph and Disaster 1945-1964''|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Lj13AAAAMAAJ|date=April 1985|publisher=Houghton Mifflin|isbn=978-0-395-36004-0|pages=596–597|access-date=2017-01-30|archive-date=2014-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140706183122/http://books.google.com/books?id=Lj13AAAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>
